textus complexus



The Poetics of Translation and Emerging Complexity


textus complexus investigates how language shapes thought
through hybrid forms—merging poetry, science, and cultural systems
to systematize multiplicity via layering, modularization,
and indexing—amplifying complexity's generative potential.
